*Djece* je u školu odlazilo uobičajeno. (The children were going to school as usual.)

Nastavnik se smiješio *djece*. (The teacher was smiling at the children.)

Nekoliko *djece* se igralo u parku. (Several children were playing in the park.)

*Djeci* su donijeli slatkiše. (They brought sweets for the children.)

*Djeci* su rekli da ne plaču. (They told the children not to cry.)